  <div class="row featurette">
    <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-offset-2 centered">
      <h1 class='text-center'>Welcome to FamilyStory!</h1>
      <br>
      <p class="lead">You know those stories that all families have? FamilyStory is the place to share them!</p>
      <p class="lead">It collects those stories from each family member in their own words and builds a narrative history of a family to last for generations to come.</p>
      <p class="lead">It's a small way to create a broad picture of a family, to keep a record of it's many stories and to connect&mdash;over time and space&mdash;with those who mean the most.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="featurette-divider">

  <br>

  <h1 class="featurette-heading text-center">How it Works</h1>

  <br><br>

  <div class="container marketing">

    <div class="row">

      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <center><i class="fa fa-thumbs-o-up fa-5x"></i></center>
        <center><h2>First, join the family!</h2>
        <p>Create a profile as a family member with your info and a short biography. This will be your own story and a way for distant relatives to read about who you are.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <center><i class="fa fa-video-camera fa-5x text-center pagination-centered"></i></center>
        <center><h2>Next, record a video!</h2></center>
        <p>This is where you answer questions about your most memorable family moments. Then, you can see how everyone else answered the same questions!</p>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <center><i class="fa fa-comments fa-5x text-center pagination-centered"></i></center>
        <center><h2>Then, add to the story!</h2></center>
        <p>Comment on any other family member's profile. This is where you share your stories about others or just record your thoughts and memories of a family member.</p>
      </div>

    </div><!-- /.row -->

    <br><br>

    <hr class="featurette-divider">

    <br><br>

    <div class="row featurette">

      <div class="col-md-5 col-md-offset-1">
        <%= image_tag "bottompic.jpg", :class => "featurette-image img-responsive" %>
      </div>

